{"tid":2462114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜限定心事台 (114)","createTime":"2021-03-25T20:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T21:18:58.000Z","uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bad08207e00734c265aa79a2800f8dd35126f0","tid":2462114,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:52:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>許願樹!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙女需要眼鏡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n?!?!都想要眼鏡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n木星要發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熊要熊啤啤同埋訓教唔好再俾人阻住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n村西透可以做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正字GPA爆4同埋搵到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腳腳繼續GPA爆4入UST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n料快啲有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWiedersehen識好多仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夢要身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n春野可以同女神一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柴子考好ielts搭火箭去木星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙鹿搵到個正常既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n范統可以順利入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCake要寧濫勿缺 搵到啱既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女生快高長大 學業進步 身體健康 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腦盧生日前岀pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">其實我諗我都係想身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老規矩<br />\n有心事又好無聊又好都可以放低係到<br />\n如果無見到無覆到麻煩提一提我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想有心事私下傾可以加我tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/lingdong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flingdong&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=b03fd84a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lingdong</a><br />\n所有野絕對保密<br />\n不過會覆得都好慢<br />\n有可能會過一兩日先覆你<br />\n因為我應該都係回post優先同有自己野要做<br />\n只要你放低我就會覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果太多人搵/我真係覆唔到回forward俾木星"},{"pid":"9f41939cb9f7ae638cf0351432df5309850671b6","tid":2462114,"uid":288105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:53:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"17a25a164d2cd68d0ee702b7bb8ff4fa98831917","tid":2462114,"uid":14269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:53:18.000Z","msg":"一收工就搶左1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9277ca79d39c5bc1c4a2e0db890ac0b154984604","tid":2462114,"uid":244329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd0cebf95147a90bf260ade4e717b3db132a1af","tid":2462114,"uid":199704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:54:19.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2942b1c13ff0f235ae44fc2daf6a9325aaa195","tid":2462114,"uid":2365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311e0696974c614e334941d9675aacd7ff0a862d","tid":2462114,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20